Supp. 568, 572-73 (D.Md.1975); Report of the Attorney General's National Committee to Study the Antitrust Laws 34-35 (1955); 
cf.  United States v. Citizens & Southern Nat'l Bank, 422 U.S. 86, 113-14, 95 S. Ct. 2099, 45 L. Ed. 2d 41 (1975).

 asserted against the plaintiffs in this action, two of the patents, Nos. 3,137,119 and 3,382,656, have been held invalid by Judge 
